    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The Mental Health Flexible Pen is the ideal choice for safety minded institutions and agencies as there is virtually no way to utilize these pens as a deadly weapon, they are essential tools for hospitals and health centers where patients may be prone to hurting themselves or others around them. These mental health flexible ballpoint ink pens are 4.25&quot; in length. Are completely flexible with no hardened plastic. Can write up to 3500 feet of long term use and can be disposed or reused at your own discretion. The non-lethal characteristics of the flexible office ball point writing pen is the only option for inpatient health care clinics, addiction specialists, psychology wards, and those working in any type of medical professional field</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Bendable Mental Health Non-Lethal Flexible Ball Point Pen (Multi-Packs)</h2>\n  <p>The Mental Health Flexible Pen is the ideal choice for safety minded institutions and agencies as there is virtually no way to utilize these pens as a deadly weapon, they are essential tools for hospitals and health centers where patients may be prone to hurting themselves or others around them.</p>\n  <p>These mental health flexible ballpoint ink pens are 4.25&quot; in length. Are completely flexible with no hardened plastic. Can write up to 3500 feet of long term use and can be disposed or reused at your own discretion.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>This flexible rubber ballpoint ink pen is an essential writing instrument for patients in hospitals and health care centers where patients may be prone to hurting themselves or others</li>\n    <li><strong>WRITING CAPACITY:</strong> Each pen contains a ink tube with a capacity of writing up to 3500 feet</li>\n    <li><strong>NON-LETHAL BENDABLE PEN:</strong> Constructed to be flexible this ballpoint black pen will bend under the slightest pressure with the tip not exceeding more than 2mm</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Length: 4.25&quot; ; Weight: 0.001 oz. ;Ink Color: Black</li>\n    <li><strong>COST EFFECTIVE BULK PENS:</strong> These ink pens are available in large quantities. Each pack size is discounted in tiers</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/covert_tactical/PP_prison_pen_lifestyle_v3ish_06.jpg\" alt=\"The Mental Health Flexible Pen is the ideal choice for safety minded institutions and agencies as there is virtually no way to utilize these pens as\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> FBPP13-2</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 706569612592</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The non-lethal characteristics of the flexible office ball point writing pen is the only option for inpatient health care clinics, addiction specialists, psychology wards, and those working in any type of medical professional field.</p>\n  <p>These pens are reliable; made with a soft rubbery material that bends under the slightest pressure, making it nearly impossible to do lethal damage with.</p>\n  <p>Ink color is available in black or blue.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
